\f2\b \cf0 \strokec2 The practical takeaway for your project
\f3\b0 \
Your current rule-based approach is the right starting point. The natural evolution would be: once you've collected enough categorized emails over several months, 
\f4\i that data
\f3\i0  becomes your training set if you ever want to move toward a smarter model. So the way you're building this now is actually setting you up well for an NLP version later if you need it.\
